	   <tr><td colspan=2> Shackle of dust<br>turn in your newbie note to the mater and boom !, if you lost it by time you need to hand it in make a new monk and get him the dust shckle and then hand in that and then log in the real monk and turn in the rest and you still recive the reward. Kinda MQing with yourself.<br><br> clay shackle (the master in far end of courtpain)<br>sabortoth cub canine - in omen right outside gates about 10 minute spawn (look for sabortooth CUB) dont drop every time shouldnt take that long.<br><br>froglok skipping stone<br>swamp of no hope of froglok skipper at the firs friend just off the gates. Shouldnt take more than 1 hour , semi rare drop.<br><br>large scorpion pincher<br>the pit, drops everytime VERY easy. of large scorion *doh*<br><br>um and one other thing cant remember sorry dont got alot of time just trying to make these simpler.<br><br>shackle of stone<br>2iksar bandit masks from the pit<br>may need help, rare spawns be patient in about 150minutes I got two. Turn in these two shackles + the shackle of copper and dust for your shackle of steel.<br><br> shackle of ROCK (hardest one IMO) ( master niska)<br><br>she wants the fists of talon southpaw. he was a freak with 2 left hands and one right.<br><br>FIST ONE - drops of sarnark courier in lake of omen. rare spawn. bring trackers (right hand)<br><br>FIST TWO - go to iksar master in timorous he gives you a bag he wants these items combine and gave backt o him for one left hand.<br><br>Intact brutling choopers (skulking BRUTLING in Walksik Woods) rare just wonder the zoned edges you will find one, i killed 3 till i got an INTACT one.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br>pitfighter gloves - random spawn through WW <br>the gobby fort is best though this took me like 9 hours , drops everytime though, kill em all anything can be a PH (place holder)<br><br>Torn sash from exiled human monk (young ronin in SrO bring trackers guess its rare but took me about 15 seconds literally.